<br>
She knew she was in the right place, but she couldn't let out the others position. Quietly, she climbed down from her tree, taking to a side near the others that was vacated and seem to be pretty well secluded.<br>
<br>
Once she'd positioned herself, Dess let out a wolf howl. To let Aly, Dawn, and the others know the young Scynthian had come to aid them in there fight against the Roman men.<br>
<br>
Though, she only knew Aly and Dawn would recognize her, she knew her other sisters would catch on quickly that the young Vasilissa was here to help the two. <p>÷ Odessa Sayler Loire ÷<br>
