<br>
And with that, Hippolyte let out the wild cry of attack to her athelfi.  Gripping a vine and wrapping it around her wrist, she seemed to fly down upon and suddenly land behind one of the soldiers.  She pulled up one of her talon daggers and ripped it right across the front of the man's throat.  Bringing him down. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

